it, it's right here.

00:00:47.420 --> 00:00:51.470
And it took me, it looks like
four or five pages, yeah.

00:00:51.470 --> 00:00:53.750
It took a lot of pages
and I ended up with this.

00:00:53.750 --> 00:00:55.690
I was able to make the graph

00:00:55.690 --> 00:00:57.410
by adding together a bunch of waves

00:00:57.410 --> 00:00:59.990
and to demonstrate that, I created this.

00:00:59.990 --> 00:01:01.630
I had to get a tripod,
here's my flip book.

00:01:01.630 --> 00:01:03.720
