00:01:03.720 --> 00:01:05.960
and then we add another
one and you can see,

00:01:05.960 --> 00:01:09.040
the more waves you add together,

00:01:09.040 --> 00:01:11.670
the closer the function gets

00:01:11.670 --> 00:01:12.860
to what you're supposed to make,

00:01:12.860 --> 00:01:14.910
because you can see that
and that look very similar.

00:01:14.910 --> 00:01:16.410
